{"tid":527573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人睇完與神同行覺得好一般","createTime":"2018-01-12T19:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T15:42:01.000Z","uid":152712,"like":48,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c948ececd6813090b8e4a0439f8e493321ee32","tid":527573,"uid":152712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T19:58:27.000Z","msg":"唔係話爛 不過各方面都好一般 <br />\n特別係劇情表達方面<br />\n鏡頭<br />\n催情位(除左臨未個場) <br />\n<br />\n個人覺得好嘅催情位除左配樂特技外<br />\n要慢慢比觀眾入戲 好似温水煮蛙咁<br />\n要show to觀眾  而唔係由對白表示出嚟<br />\n有d答辯 重要係呀媽係女人嘅道理<br />\n<br />\n成套戲係特技同打鬥位較深切  <br />\n<br />\n個人比6.5分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完全唔明d港女個個又喊又神作係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27df4628f4448c48991890cb6c8f475ea402518b","tid":527573,"uid":116578,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T20:06:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得幾感動 一次過意外死兩個仔 仲要啞既"},{"pid":"602f6a1af1f1b30d53a8b18bcfdd3e3cde86b9c8","tid":527573,"uid":152712,"like":6,"dislike":18,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T20:10:54.000Z","msg":"可能有d人話<br />\n套戲講左好多人生大道理 又有好多倫理 哲學係入面<br />\n我唔否認尼㸃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過龜兔賽跑都有好多道理  咁係咪神戲;-<br />\n<br />\nWhat I am going to say is<br />\n<br />\n電影唔係故事  電影更着重表達手法<br />\n<br />\n角色成長   配角主角之間比較 電影 幕<br />\n與幕之間切換  將唔同理論 主意 包裝比觀眾<br />\n與神同行都做得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be8c4d339a019488ae5e5678e83cae33d77d244","tid":527573,"uid":152712,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T20:16:39.000Z","msg":"如果要講一套 又係大道理 但成套戲循序漸進show 出尼  冇刻意煽情  令觀眾身同感受<br />\n連登仔應該好熟悉 about time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65f178bea684ecd3ddb1c16d4891c7d7bb93a06","tid":527573,"uid":152712,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T04:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be31cd4b2ce7b87924658a47a160387492b10a1","tid":527573,"uid":152712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T04:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff861a37fb243af15a82a48b9595d05923935493","tid":527573,"uid":53834,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T16:02:51.000Z","msg":"唔係話套戲差<br />\n但d傳媒真係過份吹捧令人反感<br />\n套戲娛樂性不足<br />\n講感動，近期睇既胰臟wonder同coco感動得多，個人認為呢套戲實在太矯情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61679e930de3194f52777f610d94e3